    "text": [
        "Dear sir,",
        "I am nicks batsman Mother; student at French Classes. I am writing, letter to ask your help in providing some extra classes to my son.",
        "Although, has always been a dedicated child but due to lack of learning ability by birth his grasping power is little slow comparable to children of same age. Moreover, ours is an English speaking family we are unable to support him in learning French at home.",
        "I would also be grateful to you, if you can enlighten me about your teaching experience and methodology used to teach students. As this will help me to evaluate the effectiveness of study plan. Further, I want to suggest that it will be beneficial for my son and other students as well to have extra classes in early morning as well. Since summer vacations are going on so I will leave it is possible for all the students to take classes twice a day , including more practice and test sessions.",
        "I hope that I will take up my advice positivily and will make necessary arrangements.",
        "Looking forward to your reply.",
        "Your sincerely,",
        "Meenakshi Kalyan"
    ],
